          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "In the 83Ge measurement a CD2 target with thickness",
                "of 430 microgramm/cm2 was used.",
                "In 85Se measurement a CD2 target with thickness",
                "of 200 microgramm/cm2 was used."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "IOCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Gas-filled ionization chamber was positioned",
                "downstream of the target to stop, count, and",
                "identify the A = 82 beam components using standard",
                "energy loss techniques"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SISD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "A large-area silicon detector array, SIDAR was",
                "positioned to cover the backward laboratory angles",
                "theta = 105.0-150.0 deg, which corresponds to",
                "c.m. angles theta c.m. =36.0-11.0 deg. The whole",
                "array covers approx. Pi steradians in the laboratory.",
                "In the 85Se measurement, another silicon detector was",
                "placed to cover the angular range of theta",
                "lab = 160.0-170.0, theta c.m. = 10.0-5.0 deg."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "Protons from (d,p) transfer reactions were",
                "detected in time coincidence (with time resolution",
                "aprox. 80 ns) with the appropriate beamlike recoil",
                "in the ionization chamber. Inverse kinematics was",
                "used."
              ]
            }
          ],
